title: Celine Dion - On Ne Change Pas [2005][DVDRIP]
description: Most Celine Dion fans are familiar with the English-language work of the Quebec-born singer. After all, this is a chart-topping artist who is renowned for her soaring power ballads and can command an impressive Las Vegas performance run. But many listeners are unaware of the French-language aspect of Dion&#039;s career, when, in fact, the emotive vocalist has recorded numerous albums in her native tongue. ON NE CHANGE PAS aims to give this material wider exposure with a well-selected retrospective of music videos and live performance clips for Dion&#039;s Gallic hits.
